`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- Using `affectsGameplay = true` as the default parameter in `drainStamina` is a non-breaking change — all existing call sites work unchanged, and only new callers that pass the flag into exploration mode benefit.
- Keeping `isExplorationMode()` in the config loader (not the store) means it can be used by any system without importing React/Legend State, maintaining the "pure functions" constraint for game systems.
